column2: Aureldi means "Away-elf" and is a name for the Amanyar Elves.
the name is from the Sindar point of view
column3: since it refers to the Elves who departed Beleriand for Aman.

column1: The Vanyarin form is Oazel and Auzel and incorporates oar "away" and eldar "Elv". It derives from *awazeld-
